manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Make It on the Counter AIR FRY TOASTER OVEN This versatile air fry oven maximizes space to deliver incredible results. The compact design features dual heating elements that ensure your food cooks quickly and evenly. Plus, the healthy ceramic nonstick pan is free of PFAS, so you can make every meal simple. From toasting bread and baking cookies to reheating leftovers and air frying your favorites, this oven delivers incredible meals with effortless style. Free of PFAS HEALTHY CERAMIC NONSTICK PAN This versatile oven’s baking pan features our easy-to-clean ceramic nonstick coating, which is specially made for electrics, derived from sand, and free of PFAS, PFOA, lead, and cadmium for effortless release and quick cleanup. Tackle Any Meal POWER YOUR COUNTERTOP COOKING The two heating elements heat all angles to deliver faster, more even results. You’ll be able to bake crusty breads, melty cookies, juicy chicken, and so much more! Two Heating Elements FIND YOUR SETTING The adjustable time and temperature dials keep cooking simple and ensures perfect results. Just set your time and temp, the dual heating elements will heat quickly and evenly so your meal cooks just right. Spacious & Versatile INCREDIBLE VERSATILITY Fits 4 slices of bread, 9” pizza, a batch of cookies, leftovers, and so much more. The spacious interior and versatile accessories (air fry basket, rack, and baking tray) ensure you have everything you need to cook on the counter. Easy Cleanup MINIMIZE THE MESS The crumb door opens for easy cleaning and the interior wipes clean with ease. Plus, the rack and air fry basket feature a PFAS-free nonstick for easy cleaning while the baking tray features our signature ceramic nonstick for mess-free performance.

SIMPLIFY EVERYDAY COOKING This countertop hero is ready to satisfy everyone’s tastebuds– from toasting bread in the morning to baking a pizza and cookies at night. INDICATOR LIGHT Once the timer is set, the indicator light illuminates so you’ll always know when the oven is on. REDUCE CLUTTER The compact design has a small footprint without sacrificing performance and style. WATCH THE ACTION The heat-resistant window makes checking your food safe and easy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I am in love
reviews.reviewText: This toaster oven with air fryer function is probably my best Amazon purchase ever. The color is super cute, size is perfect for my small counter space and it works great. Used it every day since I got it three days ago. I made a casserole, heated up food for dinner and fixed a Cornish hen ( that’s as big as you can go).Perfect for a single person. I really ordered it for the color and reasonable price but it is just perfect. If you are debating buying it, just do it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars What I expected
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I was looking for a cute usable countertop air fryer to replace my big ninja 9in1 that is annoying to get out and put away each time. It’s too big and ugly to leave out. This is super cute goes with my aesthetic and is the perfect size. I can roast a bagel or two slices of bread. I’d say it’s for a 1-2 person household if you like to use the oven to reheat lunch or leftovers. It does get warm/hot on the outside but it hasn’t been an issue or damaged anything.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The perfect compact air fryer and oven!
reviews.reviewText: I have to say… I purchased this primarily as a small oven… For toasting, reheating, convenience. But I was stunned at how amazing the air fryer function works. We’ve been using now for air fried recipes. Crispy french fries, homemade chicken nuggets, even chicken wings! I have an air fryer that’s really big and uses a lot of countertop space, I’m happy that this air fry oven does the work of two appliances. Plus it cleans up much easier! Were using it all the time. If it’s quickly, super easy to use, and I love that it’s worry-free free nonstick. It comes with a great nonstick pan that has a Ceramic Nonstick surface… and a nonstick air fry basket as well! All this and a great price! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect toaster oven
reviews.reviewText: This toaster oven is so very handy! I am finding that I use it everyday. The air fryer setting is great to make food crispy. My only complaint is that the timer isn’t digital so it’s not as easy to set. But the pink color matches my kitchen decor and it’s so cute!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute, practical and does the job... only it came with a dent.
reviews.reviewText: This was a great option for my kitchen and the color was so cute. It bakes well, I bought it for my polymer clay projects. I was pretty excited to use it, until I noticed a dent on its side as soon as I opened the box. I gave the over I try and was pleased with it, but I couldn't get over the dent it had on its right side, so I decided not to keep it. The return process was a breeze and the dent must've been a delivery thing, so sad because the oven is super cute, practical and it works as it should. Apart from the dent issue I had, I'd say the oven is a keeper! 👍
